IssuedTokenParametersElement Class

Definition

Represents a configuration element that specifies additional settings for an issued token. This class cannot be inherited.

In this Article

public sealed class IssuedTokenParametersElement : System.ServiceModel.Configuration.ServiceModelConfigurationElement
